<section id="welcome">
    <!-- IMAGE BACKGROUND -->
    <div id="welcomeImage"></div>
    <!-- HEADER BEGIN -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2 class="title">Hi, I'm Gordon</h2>
                <div class="subtitle">
                    <p>I'm a product guy who builds startups for a living.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="about" class="section--white text-xs-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
                <h5 class="section--title">About</h5>
                <p>There are two main reasons for this site's existence.</p>
                <p>First, I've wanted to create up a personal site for a quite awhile now, so <code>hello world</code>. Second, I'd like to use this site as the boilerplate for a bunch of frontend experimentation.</p>
                <p>So, that's why the site's here, but you may also be wondering who I am.<p>
                <p>While its potentially unhealthy, I feel that the answer to that question is probably best answered with what I do for a living. Currently, I'm employed at a place called <a href="#work">Wirkn</a> where I head up the product & engineering team.</p>
                <p>When I started school nearly 10 years ago excited about a future in mechanical engineering, I never imagined that someday I'd leave it behind to instead create software from my couch.</p>
                <p>But, thanks to handful of meaningful co-op expieriences at <a href="https://uwaterloo.ca">UW</a>, some seriously hard work and a bit of dumb luck I've found success in the product end of the startup world and have massively enjoyed breathing life into new products for the better part of the last decade.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="work" class="section--grey text-xs-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-xs-center">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h5 class="section--title">
                    Work
                </h5>
            </div>
            <% @projects.each do |project| %>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <%= image_tag project.image, class:"card-img-top", alt:"codego" %>
                    <div class="card-block">
                        <h4 class="card-title"><%= project.title %></h4>
                        <p class="small"><%= project.date %></p>
                        <p class="card-text"><%= project.description %></p>
                        <% if project.link.present? %>
                            <%= link_to "View Site", project.link, target: "_blank", class: "btn btn-block btn-primary" %>
                        <% else %>
                            <%= link_to "Site Shut Down", project.link, target: "_blank", class: "btn btn-block btn-secondary disabled", disabled: true %>
                        <% end %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% end %>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTACT FORM -->
<%= render partial: "contact" %>
<%= render partial: "layouts/footer" %>
